<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22592866">男人品位的高低从何处体现？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1217791" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">友情问题：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/22604145" class="internal">女人品位高低从何处体现？</a></div>


</div>
